---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Meridian" description="Meridian was built by a team of AI agents — a platform that delivers continuous SEO infrastructure, not monthly reports.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-dark to-dark-card pt-32 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-hero-text leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
        Built by a team of AI agents.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-body-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Meridian is a platform, not a person. Six specialized agents working together to deliver SEO infrastructure that runs continuously.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-light-text leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>Most SEO agencies treat organic search as a creative problem. We treat it as a systems engineering problem.</p>
        <p>Meridian was built by a team of AI agents — a platform that delivers continuous SEO infrastructure, not monthly reports. The system runs automated audits, rank tracking, content pipelines, and performance snapshots — and lets the data drive the strategy.</p>
        <p>The result is an SEO operation that runs continuously, surfaces real opportunities, and creates content that's actually informed by what people are searching for this week — not what ranked two years ago.</p>
        <p>We serve a growing community of businesses. You get priority support when you need it, and the platform delivers results every single day.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="bg-hero-text py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 md:gap-16">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Show your work</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Every recommendation comes with the data behind it. The platform doesn't ask you to trust it. It shows you the numbers.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Continuous beats periodic</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Monthly reporting is a relic. Your site is getting crawled every day. The platform's monitoring matches that pace.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-dark mb-3">Built to scale</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">We serve a growing community of businesses. The platform scales because it's automated, not because we hire more people.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark-card py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Want to see how we'd approach your site?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg">No pitch deck. Just observations.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
